name: MoMo Key
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Keys can be obtained by staking LPs or stablecoins (BEP20) into MOBOX Crates. Those keys then unlock chests which mint unique NFTs on the MOBOX.io Platform.
